Require list:

1. cmake ( sudo apt-get install cmake )
2. FLAC - libflac++-dev
3. PAI - lua ( sudo apt-get install liblua5.1-0-dev )
4. ImageMagic - 


### for developers
ln -s /data/siegerstein/admin/lang/libsml/src /usr/include/libsml



